      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Clean, honest driver offered at a fair price. This is a solid car for someone who wants something usable and presentable, but it\u2019s not perfect and should be approached as a fair-condition vehicle with some age, wear, and sorting still to be expected. A good candidate for someone realistic who wants an enjoyable car without paying top-tier money.",
