    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Exceptional mint-condition example that presents about as well as you could hope for. The exterior shows extremely well, the interior is exceptionally clean and well-kept, and the car runs and drives exactly as it should. This is the kind of vehicle that has clearly been cared for properly, with only the slightest signs of age or use if any at all. A buyer should expect a standout, turn-key car that is ready to enjoy immediately.",
