    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "A practical, budget-friendly vehicle for buyers who want dependable transportation without a big upfront cost. This car shows its age, but it still offers solid value as an affordable daily driver, work commuter, or starter vehicle. If you\u2019re looking for a straightforward purchase with room to personalize and maintain over time, this is a smart opportunity at an accessible price.",
      "price": 5995.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of potential? This car is being sold in poor condition, so I want to be upfront: it\u2019s not perfect and will suit someone handy with repairs, after a project, or needing a cheap runabout. That said, it\u2019s a complete car with lots of life left for the right buyer, and at this price it\u2019s a great chance to get into something without spending a fortune. Honest sale, priced to move, and well worth a look if you know what you\u2019re after.",
      "price": 4800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Honest, mechanically straightforward car with a strong-running engine, smooth-shifting drivetrain, and solid road manners. Not a showroom piece, but it\u2019s a dependable platform that starts up, tracks well, and delivers exactly what you want in an affordable daily, backup car, or project base. The chassis feels composed, the powertrain pulls cleanly, and it\u2019s clear this one has been kept serviceable rather than neglected. If you want usable transportation with good bones and plenty of life left for the next owner, this is a compelling value.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Honest beater with solid value. Not pretty, but it gets the job done. Priced to move at $7,900.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of honest, road-worn character you can spot from across the lot\u2014the sort of machine that still has stories left to tell. It\u2019s an affordable way into ownership for someone who values grit, usefulness, and the satisfaction of bringing out a vehicle\u2019s next chapter. Whether you need a budget-friendly runabout, a practical spare, or a hands-on project with personality, this one offers real potential at a price that leaves room to make it your own.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Honest, affordable, and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle is a practical choice for buyers seeking dependable transportation at a budget-friendly price. It shows its age cosmetically, but it delivers strong value for anyone who wants a straightforward car without the premium cost. A smart option for a commuter, first-time buyer, or anyone looking for inexpensive everyday mobility.",
